# Pin this repo's installs to the canonical npm registry. Vellum publishes with --provenance and
# advertises a zero-dependency / supply-chain-clean posture, so its committed package-lock.json must
# resolve from registry.npmjs.org (not a personal mirror) — otherwise CI's `npm ci` gate and the
# release publish step would depend on a third-party mirror's reachability.
registry=https://registry.npmjs.org/
